{"word":"ἦ 1","slug":"ἦ 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n46571\" key=\"h)=1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἦ</orth>, <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos>, never in the form <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἦε </foreign>(<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἠέ</etym>): <sense n=\"I\" id=\"n46571.0\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> TO CONFIRM an assertion, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in truth, of a surety</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ ὀλίγον οἷ παῖδα ἐοικότα γείνατο Τυδεύς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:800\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.800</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc.; ironically, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:229\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.229</biblScope></bibl>, al.; with concessive force, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">it is true that . . </tr_>: hence, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">although . . </tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ καὶ γένει ὕστερος ἦεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:215\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.215</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: freq. strengthd. by the addition of one or two other Particles, as <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ ἄρα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:24:193\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.193</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ ἄρα δή</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:446\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.446</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ ῥα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:82\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.82</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ ῥά νυ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:215\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.215</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ γάρ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:78\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.78</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ γάρ τοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:16:199\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.199</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ δή</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:272\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.272</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ δή που</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:583\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.583</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ δῆτα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-gr